text:
Ever since the theme song for Disney’s upcoming Ducktales hit the internet, we haven’t gotten it out of our heads!

Did you know that the singer who performs the song is Stuck in the Middle star Malachi Barton‘s mom, Felicia?!

“Check it out!!! My mom @feliciabarton is singing the new theme song for @disneyxd ‘s @ducktalestv,” Malachi proudly announced on his Instagram last week, adding the best hashtag of them all: “#rockstarmom”.





You probably know Felicia pretty well too — she’s one of the talented singers who performed with Ray Chew Live on Dancing With The Stars!

Listen to the theme song below!
title: Who Sings The New 'Ducktales' Theme Song? Felicia Barton, 'Stuck In The Middle' Star Malachi Barton's Mom!
